text.tspan: Stability, both for himself and his children
Wants to see his kids often. Hopes Gautam
and his family can get a job in Cleveland
so they dont have to move away; plane
Wishes Erica would chill out a bit
Wants kids to be successful, doesnt realize why theyre not
Looking for a purpose; made it in life but doesnt know
Wishes he had a bit of a sense of the outside world;
Cleveland has had immigration only recently so it remains
Loves to get around easily; used to bike more but
those days may be behind him a bit.
Unitarian values from his early days have stayed
